    <item>
      <title>沃尔沃（Volvo）汽车将萨缪尔森（Samuelsson）担任首席执行官两年期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/volvo-car-brings-back-hakan-samuelsson-as-ceo-for-two-year-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔沃汽车AB表示，哈克恩·萨缪尔森（Hakan Samuelsson）于2012年至2022年担任首席执行官，他将夺回舵手，因为瑞典汽车制造商试图导航其迫在眉睫的美国关税，使其摆脱困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/volvo-car-brings-back-hakan-samuelsson-as-ceo-for-two-year-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 15:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西非军政府的进口征税终止了免税区域访问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/west-african-juntas-import-levy-ends-duty-free-regional-access</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马里，尼日尔和布基纳法索对来自邻国进口的进口提出了新的关税，结束了西非几十年的货物自由流动政权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/west-african-juntas-import-levy-ends-duty-free-regional-access</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 13:58:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚提高了今年的预测商品出口收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/australia-raises-forecast-commodity-export-income-for-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚增加了今年对商品出口收入的预测，但随着全球需求降低将价格降低，其降低的前景持续到本十年末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/australia-raises-forecast-commodity-export-income-for-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 13:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他希望新的关税将买家送往美国汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/trump-tells-nbc-he-couldn-t-care-less-about-higher-auto-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，如果汽车制造商筹集价格，他希望消费者迁移到美国制造的汽车上，以应对他发誓要强加的所有进口车辆和零件的25％关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/trump-tells-nbc-he-couldn-t-care-less-about-higher-auto-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 23:21:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国雇主将刹车作为关税政策昏暗的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/us-employers-tap-brakes-as-tariff-policy-dims-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国的雇主可能在三月份缓和了他们的招聘，就像消费者变得越来越谨慎，经济前景对较高关税的后果的担忧感到沮丧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/us-employers-tap-brakes-as-tariff-policy-dims-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
